5:
...And after my ship sank, I found 
myself here in another world. Ever 
since, I've put my all into becoming 
the best adventurer I can be.
6:
So much for that, though. I ALWAYS 
end up choking at the most important 
times.
9:
I've even garnered a reputation around 
here for it. Some people only 
know me as the "half-baked witch".
12:
Regardless, I don't think it wise to push 
yourself beyond your limits.
15:
Yeah, sorry... We would've chosen an 
easier quest if you'd told us.
19:
N-no, it's completely my fault... I 
wanted to impress you guys and, well, 
I guess I screwed that up too.
22: Hey, don't be so down on yourself.
24:
Manipulating your own shadows with 
magic? That's no easy feat! Give 
yourself some more credit.
39:
Look, see? I can even use them for 
everyday tasks—like bringing food to 
the table!
46:
...I see.
They have a personality of their own.
58:
*sigh* I guess I'm really not cut out for 
this kind of stuff, am I?
62:
Even if that were true, what's 
important is what you want to do, 
Rebecca—
66:
Wh-what's a monster from the 
Kaleidoscope doing here?!
70: Oh no... We'd better get out of here!
74:
But someone might get hurt if we 
don't do something.
78:
Indeed. Can we count on your 
support, Rebecca?
83:
M-me? But you saw how I was back 
there... I'm just a screwup.
87:
Don't worry. We'll be with you all the 
way, so just have a little faith in 
yourself!
89: I mean, you want to go, don't you?
95:
O-of course! Anything to protect the 
citizens of Palpebra!
98:
That's the spirit. Still, though... I dunno 
if we'll be able to make it in time.
106:
O darkness, slumbering in the void—
rise from the shadows! Shadow Veil!
125:
Thanks to your quick thinking, it looks 
like no one got hurt. That's some 
veteran mage energy if you ask me!
129:
V-veteran... mage? Me?
N-no... You're just being nice.
133:
B-but still, I'm glad you two were here 
to encourage me.
136:
I know there's still a lot I have to learn, 
but I hope we can continue journeying 
together!
141: Of course. The more the merrier, right?
144:
You said it. Let's all get stronger 
together!
